---
layout: art
descr: |
  This work was inspired by <a href="http://pleaseenjoy.com/projects/personal/word-as-image/">Ji Lee</a>.
  I liked so much the game that I decided to try it too, with italian words
  (for example the first three are: whale, jellyfish and dragonfly).
  Be careful, this game is <em>really</em> addictive, you will not sleep the night anymore :P
